### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取用户列表（管理员）
GET http://localhost:8080/users
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTQ0NTczNSwiZXhwIjoxNzgxNTMyMTM1fQ.SPwIWJqhQYKJu-_k3H2cL3EQjoUO7PDg4bVIOVHD8Ck

### 给用户分配角色（管理员）
POST http://localhost:8080/users/0b6c48b1-8ae0-4e2b-ba6b-a789c72dfe8e/roles
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTQ1MTY0MSwiZXhwIjoxNzgxNTM4MDQxfQ.WgTkMKqiLQh-L_9I90D3w0bBjhbAYVYexrldE7_ucyo
